---
import Text from "@/components/fundations/elements/Text.astro";
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
---

<section>
  <Wrapper variant="standard" class="py-12">
    <Text
      tag="h1"
      variant="textBase"
      class="text-foreground font-medium text-balance"
    >
      A professional association for independent UI creators.
    </Text>
    <Wrapper variant="prose" class="mt-2">
      <p>
        The UI Collective is a professional association of independent template
        and UI creators who build and sell production-quality templates, UI
        kits, component libraries, and design systems. We are practitioners,
        founders, and full-time operators in this space, united by a shared
        commitment to quality, integrity, and the long-term health of the
        industry.
      </p>
      <p>
        Membership in the Collective is meant to be a public signal: that a
        creator is known, trusted, and committed to ethical practice, respect
        for intellectual property, and doing business in good faith. The goal
        is not to create a loose badge with no meaning, but a membership body
        that carries real professional weight.
      </p>
      <p>
        We created Uicollective to establish and uphold shared standards of
        quality, ethics, and professionalism in commercial UI work, and to
        address the behaviors that damage creators, customers, and the broader
        ecosystem, including plagiarism, license violations, deceptive
        marketing, and systematic IP theft. It is a way for serious creators to
        stand together publicly and give that trust a clearer structure.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col mt-12">
        <span>Robert Austin</span>
        <span>Michael Andreuzza</span>
      </div>
    </Wrapper>
  </Wrapper>
</section>
